column3: Find the distinct breed type and size type combinations for dogs.
column8:
SELECT DISTINCT d.breed_code,
                d.size_code
FROM dogs d
JOIN sizes s ON d.size_code = s.size_code;

column3: List the first name of all the professionals along with the description of the treatment they have done.
column8:
SELECT DISTINCT T1.first_name,
                T3.treatment_type_description
FROM professionals AS T1
JOIN Treatments AS T2 ON T1.professional_id = T2.professional_id
JOIN Treatment_types AS T3 ON T2.treatment_type_code = T3.treatment_type_code;
